24 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 21, Chapter 4, Subchapter 1, is amended
25 to add an additional section to read as follows:
26 21-4-108. Leave for organ donation.
27 (a) As used in this section:
28 (1) "Living organ donor" means an individual who has donated all
29 or part of an organ and is not deceased;
30 (2) "Organ" means a human organ that is capable of being
31 transferred from the body of one (1) person to the body of another person;
32 (3) "State agency" means a department, agency, bureau, board, or
33 commission of any branch of state government; and
34 (4)(A) "State employee" means a full-time employee of a state
35 agency who has been employed with the state agency for at least twelve (12)
36 months.
